sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    title Focus Sprint Lifecycle

    actor Student
    participant Web as Web App
    participant API as Cloud Functions
    participant Tracker as Focus Tracker
    participant DB as Firestore

    Student->>Web: Start sprint
    Web->>API: POST /focusStart
    API->>DB: Create focusSessions(active)
    API-->>Web: focusSessionId

    alt Remote inference available
        Web->>Tracker: Start ML inference session
    else Fallback path
        Web->>Tracker: Start local webcam tracking
    end

    loop During sprint
        Tracker-->>Web: Focus state updates
    end

    Student->>Web: Stop sprint
    Web->>API: POST /focusStop
    API->>DB: Mark focusSessions(ended)
    API-->>Web: Stop acknowledged
    Tracker-->>Web: Final focus summary
    Web->>DB: Save focus summary

    opt Apply progression
        Web->>API: POST /gamificationApplyFocusSession
        API->>DB: Update streaks, XP, badges
        API-->>Web: Updated profile
    end

    Web-->>Student: Show recap and progress
